aquaPeralSheet.Description:
Kora is a thick Turkish Towel you can perfectly use at the beach, pool, spa, sauna, gym or bathroom. Made in jacquard traditional white and color weaving and double sided design, Kora has a Herringbone weaving, stripes and knotted fringing at each end. Highly absorbent as well fast drying, each time you wash your towel it gets softer.
